{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Scrap either EV pay-per-mile tax or Vehicle Excise Duty for EVs. Don't have both",
        "additional_details": "We think this is too much tax on just running a car. \u00a3195 is already payable annually to tax electric cars. Then around extra \u00a3300 for 10000 miles. Plus electricity used to charge car has been taxed. Please get rid of VED or pay per mile. We believe it is too much to pay BOTH",
        "background": "From 2028 electric car owners will pay BOTH VED car tax and 3p per mile. We think this will punish working people and families resulting in around \u00a3300 extra for 10000 miles on top of \u00a3195 VED tax for many EVs. It's not like the electricity to charge the car hasn't already been taxed. ",
